  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🚀 STANDALONE N8N WORKFLOW — No Backend Required\n\n**This workflow handles EVERYTHING:**\n✅ Google OAuth authentication\n✅ Session token generation (JWT)\n✅ MongoDB registration storage\n✅ File upload to Google Drive\n✅ Telegram notifications\n✅ Duplicate prevention\n\n**Required:**\n- MongoDB connection\n- Google Drive (15 GB free)\n- Telegram bot token\n- Google OAuth credentials",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 420,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "note-001",
      "name": "📌 Note — Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-60, -620]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ⚙️ Required Environment Variables\n\n| Variable | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID` | Your Google OAuth Client ID |\n| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET` | Your Google OAuth Client Secret |\n| `N8N_BASE_URL` | https://your-n8n.com |\n| `MONGODB_URI` | mongodb://... or mongodb+srv://... |\n| `MONGODB_DATABASE` | bootcamp |\n| `JWT_SECRET` | random-256-bit-secret |\n| `GDRIVE_FOLDER_ID` | Google Drive folder ID for uploads |\n| `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` | your-telegram-bot-token |\n| `TELEGRAM_ADMIN_CHAT_ID` | your-telegram-user-id |\n| `TELEGRAM_LIVE_GROUP` | https://t.me/+livelink |\n| `TELEGRAM_VIDEO_GROUP` | https://t.me/+videolink |\n| `PAYMENT_LIVE_URL` | Payment gateway link ($49.99) |\n| `PAYMENT_VIDEO_URL` | Payment gateway link ($29.99) |",
        "height": 360,
        "width": 480,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "note-002",
      "name": "📌 Note — Environment Variables",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [400, -620]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## � Payment Gateway Setup\n\n**Get payment links from your provider:**\n\n**ABA PayWay:**\n- Create payment link for $49.99 (Live)\n- Create payment link for $29.99 (Video)\n\n**Wing/Pi Pay/True Money:**\n- Generate payment request link\n- Set amount and description\n\n**Stripe/PayPal:**\n- Create payment link in dashboard\n- Set fixed amounts\n\n**Add to environment variables:**\n- `PAYMENT_LIVE_URL` = link for $49.99\n- `PAYMENT_VIDEO_URL` = link for $29.99\n\n✅ Users click → Pay → Upload receipt",
        "height": 340,
        "width": 380,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "note-003",
